A conceptual RESTful API backend built with Python (Flask/Django) for an e-commerce platform. It provides essential services for user management, product catalog, shopping carts, and order processing, designed for frontend integration.
âœ¨ Features
â—	User authentication (registration, login, RBAC for customers/admins).
â—	Product management (CRUD operations).
â—	Shopping cart functionality (add/remove items, update quantity).
â—	Order processing and history.
â—	Stock management and validation.
ğŸ’» Technologies
â—	Python 3.x
